    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――こころの『イタズラドッキリハウス』",
      "translations": {
        "en": "―― Kokoro's 'Surprise Prank House'",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "製作開始から一週間",
      "translations": {
        "en": "One week since the production began",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 1.3266666191,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_02-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "木の板はこれくらいで足りるかな～？\n電動ドライバーとネジも必要だよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wonder if this much wood will be enough~?\nI’ll need an electric screwdriver and screws‚ too‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.5666666309,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_02-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "あとはペンキと刷毛と木工用ボンドと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And also paint‚ a brush‚ wood glue……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.7333352048,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 14.0000018715
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_02-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "こころ……私達『赤崎こころのいちばんカワイイTV』\nで使うものの買い出しって聞いてたんだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kokoro…… I thought we were out shopping for\nThings to use on “Akazaki Kokoro's Cutest TV”……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_02-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "うん！　そうだよ！\nおお、この工具セット？　も買っときましょうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yep! That's right!\nOoh‚ this tool set? Let's get this too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.522382001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 23.522382001
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 27.522382001
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_02-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "買い物カートの中身は全然可愛くありませんが……\nこれで本当にスタジオを可愛く出来るんですの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The contents of this shopping cart aren’t cute at all…\nAre you sure you can make the studio cute with these?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.822382001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_02-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "誕生日バルーンとかリボンとかはいらないの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't you need something like birthday balloons or ribbons?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.7223840355,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 39.4925889928
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_02-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "んん？　スタジオの飾りつけは\nスタッフさんがしてくれるので大丈夫です！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? The staff will take care of\ndecorating the studio‚ so it’s fine!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.6592556595
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_02-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあこれは？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then‚ what’s this?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.6592556595,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 46.8815695563
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_02-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "この間決めたじゃないですか～\n『イタズラドッキリハウス』を作るんです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Didn't we decide a while ago~?\nWe’re making a ‘Surprise Prank House’!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.6149028896,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 52.7149028896
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_02-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "家でも建てるんですの！？\nほ、本格的過ぎませんこと……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are we building a house!?\nI-Isn’t this a bit too much……?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.0815695563,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 58.5149028896
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_02-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "わ、私が想像していたドッキリって風船がバーンとか\nおもちゃの虫がウジャウジャとかだったんだけどな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-What I had in mind for a surprise prank was balloons going bang‚ or\ntoy bugs crawling everywhere……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 66.7481281082
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_02-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "はあ、なんですか、そんなドキドキしないドッキリは！\nいいですか？　これはこころの誕生日企画ですよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haa? Do you think I'll be satisfied with that boring prank!\nListen‚ this is the plan for Kokoro’s birthday‚ okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.9814614415,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 75.0814614415
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_02-kkr007.m4a",
      "text": "スタッフさんに元建築士の方がいまして。それはそれは\n盛り上がり、せっかくなら～ってことになったんです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There’s a former architect among the staff. He got really excited‚ and we decided to\nGo all out since we had this chance!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.0147947748,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 82.7814614415
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_02-kkr008.m4a",
      "text": "ということで、すずにゃんと愛ちゃんがドキドキっと\n驚くような仕掛けを沢山……ふふっ、お楽しみに！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ I’ve got tons of surprises in store for Suzunya and Ai\nthat’ll make you two's hearts skip a beat… Fufu‚ stay tuned!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.7481281082,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 93.5481291254
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ひぃっ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eek…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.5481291254,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 95.2938706715
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_02-kkr009.m4a",
      "text": "さあさあ、二人とも！\n何か希望のドッキリがあったらリクエスト受付中ですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright‚ you both!\nI’m taking requests for any pranks you’d like to get!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.8272040049,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 100.5605378468
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_02-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "リクエストなんて何もありませんわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚ I don’t have any requests!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.5605378468,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 103.8938711802
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_02-ai007.m4a",
      "text": "仕掛けられる側の私達が一緒に準備をするのって\nなんだか変じゃない……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Isn’t it weird that we are preparing surprises together‚\nwhile we are going to be pranked…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 109.9019237836
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_02-kkr010.m4a",
      "text": "そうかな？\nどんなことされるかな～ってワクワクしない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is it?\nDon’t you feel excited wondering what’s going to happen~?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.1019237836,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 114.6019237836
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "しないよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.6019237836,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 116.4105612079
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_02-kkr011.m4a",
      "text": "え。でもでも、こころは二人と一緒にいた方が\nドッキリインスピレーションがわいてくるんで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh. But Kokoro gets prank inspiration\nwhen we’re together‚ so……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.8772278745,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 125.4438945412
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_02-kkr012.m4a",
      "text": "最後まで付き合ってくれると嬉しいな～\nこころのお誕生日企画なのにな～チラッ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’d be happy if you stayed with me until the end~.\nIt’s for Kokoro’s birthday‚ you know~? Glance",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.9438945412,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 133.4105673114
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_02-ai008.m4a",
      "text": "うーん……でも、サプライズを準備するのって\n普通は誕生日の人じゃない気が……",
      "translations": {
